<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Cloudprism Solutions</title>
</head>

<body
    style="font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f0f4f8;">
    <div class="email-container"
        style="max-width: 600px; margin: 40px auto; background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
        <div class="header"
            style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4a90e2, #5cb3ff); color: #ffffff; text-align: center; padding: 30px 20px;">
            <h1 style="margin: 0; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 300;">Welcome to Cloudprism Solutions</h1>
            <p style="margin: 10px 0 0; font-size: 18px; opacity: 0.8;">Your application has been registered</p>
        </div>
        <div class="content" style="padding: 40px 30px; background-color: #ffffff;">
            <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px;">Hello <%= name %>,</p>
            <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px;">Thank you for applying for the <strong
                    style="color: #4a90e2;">
                    <%= position %>
                </strong> position. We're excited to have you as a potential team member!</p>
            <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px;">Your registered email address is: <strong
                    style="color: #4a90e2;">
                    <%= email %>
                </strong></p>
            <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 10px;">Here's your unique access code:</p>
            <div class="access-code"
                style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0f4f8, #e6eef5); border: 1px solid #d1e1f1; border-radius: 8px; padding: 15px; text-align: center; font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; color: #4a90e2; margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 2px;">
                <%= access_code %>
            </div>
            <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px;">Please keep this code safe as you'll need it during the
                application process.</p>
            <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px; text-align: center;">Ready to get started? Log in to your
                account here:</p>
            <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px;">
                <a href="<%= login_link %>"
                    style="display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4a90e2, #5cb3ff); color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; padding: 12px 30px; border-radius: 25px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px; transition: all 0.3s ease;">Login
                    to Your Account</a>
            </div>
            <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 10px;">Best regards,</p>
            <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: #4a90e2; font-weight: bold;">The Cloudprism Solutions
                Team</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer"
            style="background-color: #f0f4f8; padding: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 14px; color: #666;">
            <p style="margin: 0 0 10px;">This email was sent by Cloudprism Solutions.</p>
            <p style="margin: 0;">If you have any questions, please contact us at <a
                    href="mailto:support@cloudprism.com"
                    style="color: #4a90e2; text-decoration: none;">support@cloudprism.com</a>.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>